<div>
<h2 class="font-display font-bold text-4xl mb-6 uppercase text-black">Born from Research, <br/>Fueled by Flavor.</h2>
<div class="prose prose-lg text-black font-medium">
<p class="mb-4">
                            It started with a question during our time at Google Stitch: Why do most sustainable diet initiatives fail? The answer wasn't lack of willpower—it was a lack of cultural fit.
                        </p>
<p>
                            Traditional plant-forward solutions often ask people to abandon the flavors they grew up with. OffRamp takes a different approach. We use behavioral science to swap ingredients while keeping the soul of the dish intact. It's not about giving up; it's about upgrading.
                        </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="py-24 bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
<h2 class="font-display font-bold text-4xl text-center mb-16 uppercase">What Drives Us</h2>
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
<div class="bg-white dark:bg-card-dark border-2 border-black dark:border-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-brutal hover:shadow-brutal-lg transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col items-start h-full">
<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent-orange rounded-full border-2 border-black flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-brutal-sm">
<span class="material-icons text-white text-2xl">psychology</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl mb-4">Behavior &gt; Ideology</h3>
<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                        We don't preach. We nudge. By mapping texture and spice profiles, we create plant-based swaps that satisfy the brain's reward centers just like the original meat-based dishes.
                    </p>
</div>
<div class="bg-white dark:bg-card-dark border-2 border-black dark:border-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-brutal hover:shadow-brutal-lg transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col items-start h-full relative top-4 md:top-8">
<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent-green rounded-full border-2 border-black flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-brutal-sm">
<span class="material-icons text-white text-2xl">visibility</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl mb-4">Trust &amp; Transparency</h3>
<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                        No hidden ingredients. No "mystery meat." We provide full supply chain visibility and nutritional breakdowns for every swap we suggest.
                    </p>
</div>
<div class="bg-white dark:bg-card-dark border-2 border-black dark:border-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-brutal hover:shadow-brutal-lg transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col items-start h-full">
<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent-yellow rounded-full border-2 border-black flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-brutal-sm">
<span class="material-icons text-black text-2xl">handshake</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl mb-4">Partner-Ready DNA</h3>
<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                        We aren't just an app; we're an infrastructure layer. Built to plug directly into corporate cafeterias, university dining halls, and supply chains.
                    </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
